  "prompt": "What are the best coding bootcamps?",
  "response": "The best coding bootcamps can vary depending on factors like curriculum, cost, location, and job placement rates. As of 2023, here are some widely recognized coding bootcamps:\n\n1. **General Assembly**:\n   - Offers courses in web development, data science, and UX design.\n   - Known for strong community and networking opportunities.\n   - Provides both full-time and part-time options.\n\n2. **Flatiron School**:\n   - Offers programs in software engineering, data science, and cybersecurity.\n   - Strong emphasis on career coaching and job placement.\n   - Provides both in-person and online courses.\n\n3. **Le Wagon**:\n   - Known for its web development and data science bootcamps.\n   - Offers immersive, 9-week programs.\n   - Prominent in Europe and expanding globally.\n\n4. **Hack Reactor**:\n   - Focuses on software engineering and has a rigorous curriculum.\n   - Known for high job placement rates.\n   - Offers immersive full-time programs and online options.\n\n5. **App Academy**:\n   - Offers deferred tuition plans, where students pay after getting a job.\n   - Provides full-time software engineering courses.\n   - Known for its intensive curriculum and strong job placement support.\n\n6. **Lambda School**:\n   - Offers Income Share Agreements (ISAs) where students pay after landing a job.\n   - Focuses on software engineering and data science.\n   - Provides part-time and full-time programs.\n\n7. **Ironhack**:\n   - Offers courses in web development, UX/UI design, and data analytics.\n   - Known for its global presence and various financing options.\n   - Provides both in-person and remote learning.\n\n8. **CareerFoundry**:\n   - Offers programs in web development, UX/UI design, and data analysis.\n   - Known for personalized mentorship.\n   - Offers fully online courses tailored for career changers.\n\nWhen choosing a bootcamp, consider factors such as curriculum quality, instructor expertise, student reviews, career services, and financial options. Additionally, check if the bootcamp offers a job guarantee or support with job placements.",
